	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l491">Argentinae</placeName>, 16. augusti 1553.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. P.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quae scripsi in prioribus iis literis, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495">Bullingere</persName> colende, in dies confirmantur et scriptis optimorum virorum augentur.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hor[r]enda portendaque aluit monstrum illud verius quam homo, dux <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2590">Northumbriae</placeName>: regem optimum nostrum scribit quidem fide dignus indignissime sublatum veneno.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Priusquam mortuus est, deciderunt ungues et capillitium, adeo ut plane omnem amiserat formam ali[o]qui formosissimus.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Puduit autores venefitii corpus defuncti regis spectandum in exequiis populo (ut moris est) praeponere; proinde in vivario suo palatio adiu[n]cto clam sepelierunt et iuvenem non adeo ei dissimilem, quem interfecerant ferro, eius loco spectandum posuerunt.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Haec co[n]fessus<note type="margin">a.R.: confessuus</note> est unus ex ducis <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2590">Northumbriae</placeName> filiis.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dux cum quinque filiis ac nobilibus fere viginti captus est, inter quos et dominus <persName ref="p591">Chekus</persName>, dominus doctor <persName ref="p672">Coxeus</persName> et episcopus <placeName ref="l296">Londoniensis</placeName> cum aliis tibi neque nomine neque fama notis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hos consentiisse[?] creditur atque patrocinas[s]e, ut <persName type="auto_name">Iohanna</persName>, uxor filii ducis, declarata foret regina; quodsi verum fuerit, actum est de illis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Rex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l832">Galliae</placeName> scripsit ad civitatem <placeName ref="l2235">Calais</placeName><note type="margin">a.R.: <placeName type="citizen_name">Calleß</placeName></note> et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2625">Guines</placeName><note type="margin">a.R.: <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2625">Guynes</placeName></note>, ut cives discederent sedibus sibique civitatem et castrum <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2625">Guines</placeName><note type="margin">a.R.: <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2625">Guynes</placeName></note> vacuum relinquerent; id sibi promissum fuisse a consiliariis <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830">Angliae</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dux una cum secum captivis arbitrantur huius facinoris rei.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">In <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830">Anglia</placeName> colligitur miles ad civitatem et territorium muniendum.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vereor, ne <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l862">Helvetii</placeName> vestri in nostros fuerint<note type="margin">a.R.: fuerant</note> collecti.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vides, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495">Bullingere</persName> amicissime, quam privatus sis omni expectatione tua de <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830">Anglia</placeName> nostra; proinde vide, quid statuendum de filio.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Meae aedes ei patent, nec deerit auxilium.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Bene vale et diligenter, obsecro, salutes doctos omnes, gratiasque vobis omnibus habeo ingentes pro humani[ta]te mihi ostensa.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus <persName ref="p505">Burcherus</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Dem ffurnemmen, wysen hern <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495">Heynrych Bullynger</persName>, mynem günstigen hern praedycanten.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name">Zurich</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
